  "subject": "Fix spring context regression",
  "commit_message": "Fix spring context regression\n\n- exclude jetty dependencies since they trigger\n  autoconfiguration that breaks the context\n- add a @SpringBootTest test case to make sure this\n  does not happen again in the future\n- move datasource configuration out of the applications main class\n  and into it's own @Configuration class which makes testing easier\n  and is the more standard way of doing this\n\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-3443\nChange-Id: Icec4f2646430b50b4dffb8398f4fae62955e7633\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
